snippet.title: Bug Fables 0.8 - Lurking
snippet.description:
https://paperbugdev.tumblr.com/
https://twitter.com/PaperBugDev
http://tristanalric.fr/

It's been a while, hasn't it?

We feel a bit bad about the radio silence, but progress hasn't stopped 90% of side content is done, and the story's done all the way up to the final dungeon.

More battle skills! More NPCs! More battles! 

We hope you'll stay with us as we enter the tough final stretch!
